## Constraints and Boundaries

### Technical Constraints
- Must use Nuxt.js 2 (legacy framework, no migration to Nuxt 3)
- Static site generation only (no server-side rendering)
- Client-side rendering limitations
- Browser compatibility requirements (modern browsers)

### Business Constraints
- Must comply with Saudi General Authority of Civil Aviation regulations
- Content must reflect licensed status and compliance
- Brand guidelines must be followed
- Lead generation must integrate with existing Pipedrive CRM

### Timeline Constraints
- Project is in production state
- Changes must maintain existing functionality
- No breaking changes to deployed site

